<div id="pf426" class="pf w1b he6" data-page-no="426"><div class="pc pc426 w1b he6"><div class="t m1722 x10 h5f yc6f ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">CIVIL AND RELIGIOUS LIBERTY. </div><div class="t m5 x9 h5f y200e ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m8e5 xaa he yc75 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">39 </div><div class="t m284 x74 h31 y484 ff1 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON XII.—December 21, 1895. </div><div class="t m648 x8e h1 y792 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUNDAY LAWS. </div><div class="t m1e12 x37 he y1097 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ORIGIN AND EARLY HISTORY. • </div><div class="t m3e8 x73 he yf6c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. BY whom and when was the first Sunday law on record </div><div class="t md2e x16 he y9d7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">made? </div><div class="t m10ee x5b h3b y9d7 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ans.</div><div class="t mb26 x6d he y9d6 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">—By Constantine, A. D. 321. (See note 1.) </div><div class="t m1f3 x73 he y81f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t mae3 x60 he y2db ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">By whom and when were the so-called Christian church </div><div class="t m248 x16 he y8b1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and Roman State united? (See note 2.) </div><div class="t m104a x73 he y15ec ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m61f x60 he y15ec ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">By what means was this largely effected? (See note 3.) </div><div class="t m1d77 x96 he y1254 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THEIR OBJECT. </div><div class="t mb7 x73 he y9a2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m4d8 x4e he y1255 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is Satan&apos;s object in securing Sunday laws? (See </div><div class="t m59d x16 he yaab ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">note 4.) </div><div class="t m611 x73 he y56c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m9d1 x4e he y1d5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who have been instrumental in securing them? (See </div><div class="t m443 x16 he yf7d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">note 5.) </div><div class="t m7cb x73 he y904 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m2ce x4e he y904 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What does this show? Ans.—That such laws are reli-</div><div class="t ma73 x16 he y85f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">°ions in their nature. </div><div class="t m1bd x73 he y8be ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m156f x4e he y38c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is the expressed design of those who advocate </div><div class="t md3 x3e he y2a4 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sunday laws? (See note 6.) </div><div class="t m286 x48 he y547 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m1cc x4e he y547 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For what were civil governments ordained? </div><div class="t m1923 xa8 h3b yaf1 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ans.—To </div><div class="t m31d x7f he yaf1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pro-</div><div class="t m1b0 x16 he ye87 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tect the rights of men, and not to protect religious institutions. </div><div class="t m219e x42 he y571 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THEIR RESULTS. </div><div class="t m1f3 x73 he y1624 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m59c x4e he y1624 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is the Sunday institution? Ans.—The mark of </div><div class="t ma79 x16 he y3aa ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">papal power and apostasy, the mark of the beast. </div><div class="t m1bd x5d he y90d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to. What do Sunday laws, therefore, enforce? </div><div class="t m2ae x5d he y800 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ir. Where is this mark to be received? </div><div class="t m5aa x70 h1 yaf6 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rev. 13 : 16. </div><div class="t m41c x14 he y253 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t m877 x4e he yb1d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What would the hand naturally symbolize? </div><div class="t m515 x23 h94 y253 ff6 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ans.</div><div class="t m1717 xa6 he y253 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">—Labor. </div><div class="t m723 x3e he y8f1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">See i Cora 4 : I2; Eph. 4 :28. What would be represented by </div><div class="t mab7 x16 he y54d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the forehead? </div><div class="t m219f x10 h3b y221 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ans.—The </div><div class="t mdb x47 he y52e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mind. See Rom. 7 : 25. </div><div class="t m41c x14 he y78b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t me66 x60 he y78b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Where will those receive the mark of the beast, there-</div><div class="t ma1b x16 he y4b9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fore, who cease to work on Sunday simply in deference to,the </div><div class="t mec0 x16 he y9db ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">law? </div><div class="t m637 x14 he y1207 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14: Where will those receive it who, knowing its origin, con-</div><div class="t m261 x16 he yf8c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tinue to observe it as a religious institution? </div><div class="t m225 x5d he y82f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">15. Is it not significant, therefore, that the Sunday institution </div><div class="t m19a x16 he y830 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has taken on its &quot;civil&quot; and &quot;religious&quot; aspect? (See note 7.) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
